{
  "stem": "27507.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the blockades, some of them were absolutely horrendous.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Some of them were going on for days, for two, three days, when we never dreamt of moving out of the hiding place when we had a hiding place there inside the shop.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we had-- but pretty soon, we were, as well, we found some apartment on the Schultz terrain, but not in the shop itself, but there was the one that we moved into was, I think, in [POLISH] 49.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I think it was opposite, roughly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was very near.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And it was a big flat on the maybe third floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I think it was on the third floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And the owners of the flat were not there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "The flat was empty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "All the furniture was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "All the things were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "All the stuff was still there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But the owners must have already gone to Treblinka in one of the early transports.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But if we thought that there is-- I think we spent some nights in this flat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But I think that there was-- because my uncles, as I said, were department managers, they had some prior information from Schultz, from the factory owner, if something worrying was going to happen nearby or not.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I think when there was a great worry, we would not go even out of the shop.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And when they thought that things were a bit peaceful, we would maybe go and spend a day or a night in this apartment.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "But even Schultz probably didn't know everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And even because although he was German, and although he was director of the big factory which was employing 10 or 12,000 people, the SS didn't give him all the information.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Sometimes he would get some information.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And sometimes he wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
